reviewText: Cant get enough of these western movies! We take them on camping trips too!
Great movie pack. These were a gift for my father-in-law and he loved it. He said there's a lot of great movies in there.
This is a nice selection of really classic Old Westerns, Black & White mostly, but still very nice collection
A gift for my mom and she is loving it. Lots to watch of the western outlaws.

Rustle up these bad hombres in these classic westerns. Yet another 50 movie set of westerns, this time concentrating on the outlaws of the old west fighting against the forces of law and order. This time I found an Audie Murphy classic but I'm afraid it's Apache Rifles, a movie from the latter years of his career. Would like to have found early Audie Murphy movies but this is good enough. Also, the Lone Ranger feature movie with Clayton more is on this set. I even discovered that the movie Joshua is on this set. a great classic with Fred Williamson, a rare African American cast in a major western role! So circle the wagons, make sure your pistol is loaded and happy viewing!
Perfect. Exactly as I expected. Delivery in time!
some poor copies; more info needed; some great discoveries
Bought as a gift, but from the looks of the titles, it seems to have different ones I've not seen before.  Sure he will like it.
